WEBVTT

01:40:30.649 --> 01:40:32.149
Good evening.
What is it, Philip?

01:40:32.191 --> 01:40:34.066
Sir, there's been
an interesting development.

01:40:37.774 --> 01:40:39.358
Philip, I want to see him.

01:40:39.774 --> 01:40:40.774
Understood?

01:40:41.774 --> 01:40:43.358
No, no.
Don't bring him to my office.
